parameters.name: EnsRegionId
parameters.description: The ID of the Edge Node Service (ENS) node.

parameters.name: InstanceType
parameters.description: The instance type of the NAT gateway. Set the value to **enat.default**.

parameters.name: Name
parameters.description: The name of the NAT gateway. The name must be 1 to 128 characters in length. The name cannot start with `http://` or `https://`.
